{
  "stem": "5371.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when we came to that camp, the next day they took us to Danzig to the port area to a-- a-- an island.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's called Holm, where all of ships there, battleships and submarines.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they put us up in big, like, warehouses.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they taught us how to weld plates.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we worked.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Some weeks I worked nights.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Some weeks I worked days.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we worked both shifts.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "After like three weeks, they put us up on the ships to do some welding.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I-- I knew welding like I know-- after three weeks I knew welding like I know dentistry.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyway, but I-- I knew already.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I held the mask and I hold that I thing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I know how to the distance to hold from the plate.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they put us up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I remember they put us up once in a big-- the ship was [INAUDIBLE] on the-- on the edge of the, you know, the water.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there was a ladder put up on top of the ship.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we had to climb up, you know, that big ladder into that battleship.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I was with another man.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I mentioned before I was not afraid of anything.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I was like fearless.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I came up almost on the top of the ladder, and he was down at almost in the middle.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "When you came up to the middle of the ladder, you were over the water and he wouldn't go any further.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So he went down and [? he can-- ?] they beat-- they were beating him, kicking him, but he [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "When I was up there myself, and I was welding there, not a very good job but I was welding.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So I was there-- we were there a few-- few weeks.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
